00:16:05,740 --> 00:16:06,980
Let me make a toast.

378
00:16:07,100 --> 00:16:08,740
After this year's project,

379
00:16:08,740 --> 00:16:10,460
you surely will get promoted.

380
00:16:10,700 --> 00:16:11,860
Thanks to you.

381
00:16:11,860 --> 00:16:13,340
