387
00:16:20,200 --> 00:16:21,780
Ask him. He offers the best in Shanghai.

388
00:16:21,780 --> 00:16:22,780
- No problem.
- Great.

389
00:16:22,780 --> 00:16:24,420
Let's make a toast together. Come on.

390
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:26,180
Come on.

391
00:16:26,580 --> 00:16:27,420
Come.

392
00:16:32,300 --> 00:16:34,020
