404
00:16:54,420 --> 00:16:55,420
- I know.
- Right?

405
00:16:55,420 --> 00:16:56,660
Men always look for

406
00:16:56,780 --> 00:16:57,900
housewife materials.

407
00:16:58,200 --> 00:16:59,680
Women who are as outstanding as we are

408
00:16:59,680 --> 00:17:01,300
