416
00:17:20,760 --> 00:17:22,170
Fix your teeth.

417
00:17:22,260 --> 00:17:23,500
Take folic acid supplements.

418
00:17:23,500 --> 00:17:24,480
Docosahexaenoic acid.

419
00:17:24,480 --> 00:17:25,790
And all other vitamin supplements.

420
00:17:25,790 --> 00:17:27,400
There are many things to do.
