450
00:19:26,980 --> 00:19:28,140
We don't have to wait for her.

451
00:19:28,200 --> 00:19:29,400
In order to be the team leader,

452
00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:31,180
she's working extra hard
to present herself.

453
00:19:32,420 --> 00:19:35,500
But considering her relationship
with Ms. Hu,

454
00:19:35,660 --> 00:19:37,180
