455
00:19:37,420 --> 00:19:40,180
What's her relationship with Ms. Hu?

456
00:19:40,180 --> 00:19:41,180
You don't know?

457
00:19:41,420 --> 00:19:42,660
No, I don't.

458
00:19:42,980 --> 00:19:45,140
Her boyfriend Zheng Hao's mom

459
00:19:45,740 --> 00:19:48,660
