462
00:19:51,800 --> 00:19:53,380
- So uninformed.
- I don't.

463
00:19:53,380 --> 00:19:54,980
- Let's go.
- The car has arrived. Come.

464
00:20:09,900 --> 00:20:12,100
(She works independently.)

