and confrontations.)

475
00:20:36,820 --> 00:20:39,300
(Thus, she tries even harder
to prove herself,)

476
00:20:39,660 --> 00:20:42,030
(to prove that she does not
rely on connections.)

477
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:50,450
(Ms. Hu: Speech Script.
