for a revolution.

563
00:25:35,980 --> 00:25:37,380
Sacrifice for the family?

564
00:25:37,380 --> 00:25:39,180
You're talking nonsense.

565
00:25:39,420 --> 00:25:41,180
Family is supposed to protect us.

566
00:25:41,180 --> 00:25:42,940
If we should make sacrifices for it,

567
00:25:42,940 --> 00:25:44,260
then it has become our enemy.

568
00:25:44,380 --> 00:25:46,180
When friends and family
come to a wedding,

569
00:25:46,180 --> 00:25:47,200
they should all wear black

570
00:25:47,200 --> 00:25:48,460
and pin a white flower on their chests.

571
00:25:48,740 --> 00:25:49,860
Today, let us all

572
00:25:49,860 --> 00:25:51,260
sincerely and respectfully

573
00:25:51,420 --> 00:25:52,620
mourn together

574
00:25:52,820 --> 00:25:55,660
over the poor people
who have been sacrificed for the family.

575
00:25:56,220 --> 00:25:59,580
Today another young couple
will get married tragically.

576
00:25:59,820 --> 00:26:02,460
They are to be
the victims of the family.

577
00:26:02,860 --> 00:26:05,420
Have you guys made the decision?

578
00:26:05,540 --> 00:26:07,300
Who should you sacrifice after marriage?

579
00:26:08,660 --> 00:26:10,220
Sacrifice the wife, right?

580
00:26:10,660 --> 00:26:13,260
Great! It's always the wife
who becomes the sacrifice.

581
00:26:13,380 --> 00:26:14,620
Now, friends.

582
00:26:14,620 --> 00:26:16,820
Let us pay a three-minute silent tribute

583
00:26:16,820 --> 00:26:19,580
to the bride who will be sacrificed.

584
00:26:24,060 --> 00:26:24,900
What?

585
00:26:25,180 --> 00:26:26,740
This is fun.

586
00:26:28,660 --> 00:26:30,260
Did you register at the new school?

587
00:26:30,260 --> 00:26:32,140
No. I'll do it tomorrow.

588
00:26:34,660 --> 00:26:35,660
Are you nervous?

589
00:26:36,140 --> 00:26:37,660
Why would I be nervous?

590
00:26:37,900 --> 00:26:39,220
I want to check out the new school

591
00:26:39,220 --> 00:26:40,940
and see what my new classmates
look like.

592
00:26:41,180 --> 00:26:42,060
Maybe I'll meet

593
00:26:42,060 --> 00:26:43,420
a friend like you.

594
00:26:43,860 --> 00:26:44,700
You certainly will.

