00:27:12,620 --> 00:27:13,860
Breakfast is still not ready?

610
00:27:14,180 --> 00:27:15,180
Stop nagging.

611
00:27:15,180 --> 00:27:16,100
Here.

612
00:27:18,180 --> 00:27:19,340
Come on. Here's breakfast.

613
00:27:21,140 --> 00:27:22,100
I'm not being picky.

614
00:27:22,100 --> 00:27:24,100
But can't you plan things ahead?

615
00:27:24,100 --> 00:27:26,500
Why don't you clear out
the living room first?

616
00:27:26,700 --> 00:27:27,660
The space is so limited.

617
00:27:27,660 --> 00:27:29,140
How can the three of us eat here?

618
00:27:29,140 --> 00:27:30,860
Why can't we eat here?

619
00:27:30,860 --> 00:27:33,100
How could I clear the place right away?

620
00:27:33,220 --> 00:27:35,260
It takes time to organize the room.

621
00:27:35,500 --> 00:27:37,420
I can't do it instantly.

622
00:27:37,500 --> 00:27:39,500
I've been busy for quite a while.

623
00:27:39,580 --> 00:27:40,420
Mom.

624
00:27:40,580 --> 00:27:42,660
Where are my clothes for this weather?

625
00:27:42,660 --> 00:27:44,380
My hoodies and jeans.

626
00:27:46,100 --> 00:27:47,940
They're all in that case.

627
00:27:47,940 --> 00:27:49,100
You're not a child anymore.

628
00:27:49,100 --> 00:27:50,740
Go look for them yourself.

629
00:27:51,020 --> 00:27:51,940
- Look.
- Don't get a cold.

630
00:27:51,940 --> 00:27:52,860
What have I told you?

631
00:27:52,860 --> 00:27:54,660
You need a plan.

632
00:27:54,660 --> 00:27:56,000
You have to take out

633
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:57,250
the clothes that we are to wear.

634
00:27:58,100 --> 00:27:59,580
That's how I don't have a plan?

635
00:27:59,900 --> 00:28:01,060
Why can't you

636
00:28:01,060 --> 00:28:03,340
find your own clothes?

637
00:28:03,500 --> 00:28:04,900
Isn't that your business?

638
00:28:04,900 --> 00:28:06,140
My business?

639
00:28:06,140 --> 00:28:07,380
I don't even want to move here.

640
00:28:08,340 --> 00:28:09,820
I want to stay in Shenzhen.

641
00:28:10,340 --> 00:28:11,980
You're the one who wanted to come.

