00:28:20,900 --> 00:28:23,700
(Ningxi No.7 Middle School)

643
00:28:26,500 --> 00:28:29,060
(Ningxi No.7 Middle School)

644
00:28:29,500 --> 00:28:31,100
You have to be mentally prepared.

645
00:28:31,400 --> 00:28:33,100
Because this is the class
for top students.

646
00:28:33,180 --> 00:28:35,180
So the task of studying may be heavy.

647
00:28:35,980 --> 00:28:37,620
But our classmates are friendly.

648
00:28:37,900 --> 00:28:39,980
I think you can get along well.

649
00:28:40,600 --> 00:28:42,460
Come to me if anything happens, okay?

650
00:28:45,100 --> 00:28:46,220
That's the new student?

651
00:28:46,460 --> 00:28:47,300
Biao.

652
00:28:48,900 --> 00:28:50,140
What does she look like?

653
00:28:55,980 --> 00:28:57,940
That's our class's new transfer student?

654
00:28:58,900 --> 00:29:00,220
What's the weather now?

655
00:29:00,420 --> 00:29:01,620
She's already wearing a dress.

656
00:29:02,380 --> 00:29:03,220
Attention seeker.

657
00:29:07,740 --> 00:29:10,180
Our class is welcoming
a new student today.

658
00:29:10,420 --> 00:29:13,180
I hope you will treat her
like an old classmate.

659
00:29:13,460 --> 00:29:14,460
Make her feel

660
00:29:14,460 --> 00:29:16,670
how warmly our class welcomes her.

661
00:29:17,180 --> 00:29:19,620
Welcome Wu Xiuya!

662
00:29:19,620 --> 00:29:21,700
(Advanced Class)

663
00:29:24,420 --> 00:29:25,260
Wang Zihao,

664
00:29:25,420 --> 00:29:27,140
go sit in the back row with Zhang Yang.

665
00:29:27,940 --> 00:29:29,660
Why put me next to Zhang Yang again?

666
00:29:29,980 --> 00:29:31,660
I don't want to sit next to you.

667
00:29:31,660 --> 00:29:32,500
Mr. Mu,

668
00:29:32,520 --> 00:29:34,740
the new student can sit next to me.

669
00:29:34,980 --> 00:29:36,420
Cut the nonsense.

670
00:29:36,420 --> 00:29:37,420
Hurry up and go.

671
00:29:37,420 --> 00:29:39,220
Hurry up. Go.

672
00:29:40,900 --> 00:29:41,740
Bye, bro.

673
00:29:41,740 --> 00:29:43,620
Sit next to the monitor, Shi Ye.

674
00:29:43,980 --> 00:29:45,060
- Thanks.
- You're welcome.

675
00:29:47,380 --> 00:29:49,740
Shi Ye, help the new student

676
00:29:49,740 --> 00:29:51,180
adjust to the new environment.

677
00:29:51,660 --> 00:29:52,500
Sure.

678
00:29:53,800 --> 00:29:55,220
- Alright, let's get to the class.
- Hello.

679
00:29:55,980 --> 00:29:57,660
Turn to page 78.

680
00:29:58,300 --> 00:29:59,420
In this class, we'll continue

681
00:29:59,420 --> 00:30:00,940
with space geometry.

682
00:30:04,180 --> 00:30:05,180
Class is finally over.

683
00:30:05,500 --> 00:30:06,600
Have you watched the drama?

684
00:30:06,600 --> 00:30:07,900
I stand for Yueru. How about you?

685
00:30:08,180 --> 00:30:10,380
But Ling was with Xiaoyao first.

686
00:30:10,380 --> 00:30:11,900
Why should Yueru take away Xiaoyao?

687
00:30:11,900 --> 00:30:14,440
When it comes to love,
being first doesn't mean get served first.

688
00:30:14,440 --> 00:30:16,300
That's because Li Xiaoyao
lost his memory.

689
00:30:16,300 --> 00:30:17,700
Otherwise, how can she get a chance?

690
00:30:17,900 --> 00:30:18,830
No!

691
00:30:18,840 --> 00:30:20,140
I like Lin Yueru as well.

692
00:30:20,380 --> 00:30:21,420
I think she's awesome.

693
00:30:21,660 --> 00:30:22,500
Right?

694
00:30:23,100 --> 00:30:24,740
Have you seen the episode when she died?

695
00:30:24,800 --> 00:30:25,660
She died?

696
00:30:25,660 --> 00:30:26,900
Han Qian, Liu Fangyang.

697
00:30:27,260 --> 00:30:28,180
Come here.

698
00:30:33,530 --> 00:30:34,420
What?

699
00:30:34,420 --> 00:30:35,900
We were talking to each other.

700
00:30:35,900 --> 00:30:36,740
She suddenly...

701
00:30:56,180 --> 00:30:57,100
Thank you.

702
00:31:05,900 --> 00:31:08,780
(Ningxi No.7 Middle School)

703
00:31:24,980 --> 00:31:25,980
What do you want?

704
00:31:26,980 --> 00:31:28,420
What do you mean?

705
00:31:28,460 --> 00:31:29,860
Nobody is wearing a skirt.

706
00:31:29,860 --> 00:31:30,700
Just you.

707
00:31:30,710 --> 00:31:31,820
You tell me what you want.

708
00:31:32,940 --> 00:31:35,660
I'm wearing a skirt
because I just moved here.

709
00:31:35,660 --> 00:31:37,060
My clothes haven't been unpacked.

710
00:31:37,060 --> 00:31:38,500
I only have this to wear.

711
00:31:39,220 --> 00:31:40,620
Don't try to fool me.

712
00:31:40,660 --> 00:31:42,400
Who will buy this lousy excuse?

713
00:31:42,400 --> 00:31:43,600
It's too early to wear dresses.

714
00:31:43,600 --> 00:31:44,460
No one is wearing a dress.

715
00:31:44,980 --> 00:31:46,660
You wear it when you just come here.

716
00:31:47,100 --> 00:31:47,910
It just shows

717
00:31:47,910 --> 00:31:49,150
that you're an attention seeker.

718
00:31:49,180 --> 00:31:50,460
You want to show off.

719
00:31:50,980 --> 00:31:52,660
Watch your mouth.

720
00:31:52,660 --> 00:31:54,380
I've already explained it to you.

721
00:31:54,380 --> 00:31:55,940
I have no other clothes to wear.

722
00:31:56,260 --> 00:31:58,340
Even if I wear a dress on purpose,

723
00:31:58,340 --> 00:31:59,420
what then?

724
00:31:59,420 --> 00:32:01,580
Does the school prohibit
wearing a dress?

725
00:32:01,580 --> 00:32:04,060
The school does not prohibit
wearing a dress.

726
00:32:04,060 --> 00:32:05,140
But that's because

727
00:32:05,140 --> 00:32:07,660
we all know what we should do.

728
00:32:08,060 --> 00:32:09,660
No.7 Middle School is a decent school.

729
00:32:09,660 --> 00:32:11,540
It has no place for students

730
00:32:11,540 --> 00:32:12,980
who don't study but only play around.

731
00:32:13,100 --> 00:32:14,140
I'm warning you.

732
00:32:14,180 --> 00:32:15,900
No.7 Middle School is
a complicated place.

733
00:32:15,900 --> 00:32:17,210
You've just been transferred here.

734
00:32:17,210 --> 00:32:18,660
Don't try to seek attention.

735
00:32:18,900 --> 00:32:20,660
Don't wear a dress tomorrow.

736
00:32:20,820 --> 00:32:23,420
Also, you need to ask the teacher

737
00:32:23,420 --> 00:32:25,060
to change your seat tomorrow.

738
00:32:25,060 --> 00:32:26,340
Why should I change my seat?

739
00:32:26,340 --> 00:32:29,100
Because Fang Lu doesn't want you
to sit next to the monitor.

740
00:32:29,420 --> 00:32:30,620
Stop nagging.

741
00:32:32,820 --> 00:32:35,340
You just said that No.7 Middle School is
a decent school.

742
00:32:35,380 --> 00:32:37,380
It's not a place for students
who play around.

743
00:32:37,780 --> 00:32:39,820
Then aren't you just playing around?

744
00:32:40,080 --> 00:32:41,890
You know you're contradicting yourself,
right?

745
00:32:43,620 --> 00:32:45,400
Also, I'll wear whatever I want.

746
00:32:45,400 --> 00:32:46,300
It's none of your business.

747
00:32:46,880 --> 00:32:48,060
The seat is arranged by the teacher.

748
00:32:48,060 --> 00:32:49,460
If Fang Lu is not fine with it,

749
00:32:49,460 --> 00:32:51,060
she can report it to the teacher.

750
00:32:51,220 --> 00:32:52,060
Mr. Mu,

751
00:32:52,060 --> 00:32:53,500
can you move

752
00:32:53,500 --> 00:32:54,860
the new student to another seat?

753
00:32:54,900 --> 00:32:55,740
Why?

754
00:32:55,980 --> 00:32:58,380
Because I want to sit
next to our monitor.

755
00:32:58,500 --> 00:32:59,900
See how the teacher will
respond to that.

756
00:33:00,840 --> 00:33:01,680
You...

757
00:33:02,180 --> 00:33:03,420
What did they say today?

758
00:33:04,620 --> 00:33:06,000
They said I wore a dress

759
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:07,200
because I was seeking for attention.

760
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:08,260
All nasty stuff.

761
00:33:08,380 --> 00:33:10,180
They asked me not to wear a dress.

762
00:33:10,380 --> 00:33:11,220
Well.

763
00:33:11,220 --> 00:33:12,660
That's too mean.

764
00:33:12,740 --> 00:33:13,740
Right!

765
00:33:14,060 --> 00:33:15,860
Anyway,

766
00:33:15,860 --> 00:33:18,400
I was arranged to sit
next to the monitor,

767
00:33:18,400 --> 00:33:20,060
but Fang Lu wanted to sit there.

768
00:33:20,060 --> 00:33:21,380
That's why she does not like me.

769
00:33:22,860 --> 00:33:24,620
But the monitor is nice.

770
00:33:24,740 --> 00:33:25,900
He saw I was cold today,

771
00:33:26,060 --> 00:33:27,620
so he lent me his coat.

772
00:33:27,860 --> 00:33:30,620
When he lent his coat to you,

773
00:33:30,620 --> 00:33:32,180
did you refuse?

774
00:33:33,500 --> 00:33:35,180
I did hesitate for a bit.

775
00:33:35,660 --> 00:33:37,580
He's a boy after all.

776
00:33:38,340 --> 00:33:39,300
But when I saw

777
00:33:39,300 --> 00:33:40,820
the facial expressions of those girls,

778
00:33:40,820 --> 00:33:42,900
I was so mad.

779
00:33:43,180 --> 00:33:44,020
Why?

780
00:33:44,420 --> 00:33:45,340
Why do I

781
00:33:45,340 --> 00:33:46,900
have to change my clothes

782
00:33:46,900 --> 00:33:47,860
or my seat

783
00:33:47,860 --> 00:33:49,220
at their command?

784
00:33:50,180 --> 00:33:52,060
I have to learn to say no to them.

785
00:33:52,260 --> 00:33:54,220
Otherwise, they will push it further.

786
00:33:55,340 --> 00:33:56,380
Actually, I have received

787
00:33:56,380 --> 00:33:57,940
my new school uniform this afternoon.

788
00:33:58,220 --> 00:34:00,140
But hearing her say that,

789
00:34:00,140 --> 00:34:01,820
I'll keep wearing a dress.

790
00:34:02,060 --> 00:34:05,220
Didn't you say
it's still too cold for dresses?

791
00:34:05,740 --> 00:34:08,660
I don't know
if you're smart or dumb anymore.

792
00:34:09,820 --> 00:34:10,780
It makes me a coward

793
00:34:10,780 --> 00:34:12,620
if I don't wear a dress.

794
00:34:12,740 --> 00:34:14,740
But your relationship with these girls

795
00:34:14,740 --> 00:34:15,740
will get worse.

796
00:34:16,820 --> 00:34:17,740
Let it be worse.

797
00:34:18,260 --> 00:34:20,500
People can't live on pleasing others.

798
00:34:21,610 --> 00:34:23,500
I won't live like my mom does.

799
00:34:23,500 --> 00:34:24,420
It's so upsetting.

800
00:34:27,580 --> 00:34:29,340
Mom, where's my red dress?

801
00:34:30,900 --> 00:34:31,860
Mom.

802
00:34:32,420 --> 00:34:33,740
Where's my red dress?

803
00:34:34,540 --> 00:34:36,820
It's washed.
It's in the washing machine.

804
00:35:02,820 --> 00:35:03,660
Shi Ye.

805
00:35:04,260 --> 00:35:05,100
Here's your coat.

806
00:35:08,260 --> 00:35:09,180
It's you.

807
00:35:09,500 --> 00:35:11,500
I almost couldn't recognize you
without the dress.

808
00:35:12,380 --> 00:35:13,780
I wore the dress yesterday

809
00:35:13,780 --> 00:35:15,540
because my mom forgot
to unpack my clothes.

810
00:35:15,660 --> 00:35:17,060
I almost froze to death yesterday.

811
00:35:17,060 --> 00:35:18,100
It's even colder today.

812
00:35:18,100 --> 00:35:19,220
I'm not dumb.

813
00:35:19,250 --> 00:35:21,300
The weather is indeed too chill
for wearing dresses.

814
00:35:29,580 --> 00:35:30,660
Don't you feel cold?

815
00:35:42,820 --> 00:35:43,780
- Nice.
- Nice.

816
00:35:45,580 --> 00:35:46,420
Nice one.

817
00:35:50,820 --> 00:35:51,660
Good job!

818
00:35:54,820 --> 00:35:56,740
Bro, I'm done.

819
00:35:57,100 --> 00:35:58,300
I'll get back to the classroom.

820
00:35:58,460 --> 00:35:59,340
I have homework to do.

821
00:35:59,500 --> 00:36:00,780
But we don't have enough players.

822
00:36:00,980 --> 00:36:02,100
Can I join?

823
00:36:09,900 --> 00:36:11,150
You know how to play basketball?

824
00:36:11,380 --> 00:36:13,500
What?
You don't think I can play basketball?

825
00:36:20,340 --> 00:36:21,540
Well done.

826
00:36:22,060 --> 00:36:23,180
- Can I join?
- Come on.

827
00:36:23,180 --> 00:36:24,700
- Give her the shirt.
- Sure.

828
00:36:24,980 --> 00:36:26,260
- Here.
- Bye, then.

829
00:36:26,420 --> 00:36:27,380
You're with our team.

830
00:36:27,380 --> 00:36:28,220
Sure.

831
00:36:28,230 --> 00:36:29,420
Okay. Let's go.

832
00:36:35,660 --> 00:36:37,060
- Nice one.
- Good job!

833
00:36:41,780 --> 00:36:42,620
Good job!

834
00:36:51,500 --> 00:36:52,340
Yes!

835
00:37:01,820 --> 00:37:02,660
Cool!

836
00:37:04,620 --> 00:37:06,460
One second. My sock has dropped.

837
00:37:16,180 --> 00:37:17,060
I didn't know

838
00:37:17,300 --> 00:37:18,580
you were so into basketball.

839
00:37:20,400 --> 00:37:21,650
I learned it from my best friend

840
00:37:21,650 --> 00:37:23,180
when I was in Shenzhen.

841
00:37:23,400 --> 00:37:24,790
We used to play together very often.

842
00:37:25,300 --> 00:37:27,260
Playing basketball
makes me feel relaxed.

843
00:37:28,500 --> 00:37:30,250
I also feel
that you're not your normal self

844
00:37:30,250 --> 00:37:31,300
when you play basketball.

845
00:37:31,340 --> 00:37:32,500
How's that?

846
00:37:32,740 --> 00:37:34,980
I just feel that you're your true self

847
00:37:34,980 --> 00:37:36,180
when you play basketball.

848
00:37:36,180 --> 00:37:37,260
When not playing basketball,

849
00:37:39,100 --> 00:37:40,100
you're a bit pretentious.

850
00:37:40,580 --> 00:37:41,820
How come?

851
00:37:42,180 --> 00:37:43,460
You pretend to be a good student.

852
00:37:43,460 --> 00:37:45,540
Look how neat your pencils are.

853
00:37:45,540 --> 00:37:47,300
And your clothes.

854
00:37:47,740 --> 00:37:48,740
I don't like this myself.

855
00:37:49,740 --> 00:37:50,660
But my mom asked me to.

856
00:37:51,180 --> 00:37:52,180
I heard about it.

857
00:37:52,300 --> 00:37:54,860
Your mom is our school's dean.

858
00:37:55,380 --> 00:37:56,220
Let me have a look.

859
00:37:56,900 --> 00:37:59,020
Cool. You're not beyond salvation.
There is some rebellion left.

860
00:37:59,170 --> 00:38:00,020
But not much.

861
00:38:00,020 --> 00:38:01,740
You can learn from me.

862
00:38:07,420 --> 00:38:09,180
On her first day, she was so dressed up,

863
00:38:09,180 --> 00:38:10,540
trying to seek attention.

864
00:38:10,540 --> 00:38:12,020
She even played basketball with boys.

865
00:38:12,540 --> 00:38:14,460
We'd rather die than do what she did.

866
00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:16,200
I wonder where she learned all that.

867
00:38:16,500 --> 00:38:17,780
Who knows

868
00:38:17,780 --> 00:38:18,900
why she was transferred here?

869
00:38:19,220 --> 00:38:20,100
Maybe

870
00:38:20,100 --> 00:38:22,300
she was expelled for getting in trouble.

871
00:38:22,620 --> 00:38:24,400
She was transferred here

872
00:38:24,400 --> 00:38:25,990
because she got into trouble
at her old school.

873
00:38:27,060 --> 00:38:27,900
What trouble?

874
00:38:28,200 --> 00:38:30,140
(Wu Xiuya had no idea that rumors)
Boy and girl things.

875
00:38:30,140 --> 00:38:32,380
(about her transfer)
Because she couldn't stay there.

876
00:38:32,400 --> 00:38:34,980
(were spreading like wildfire on campus.)
- Really? - It's true.

877
00:38:34,980 --> 00:38:36,220
That's awesome.

878
00:38:36,980 --> 00:38:38,380
- Look. That's her.
- It's her?

879
00:38:38,380 --> 00:38:40,020
Those things are real?

880
00:38:40,140 --> 00:38:41,260
Of course they are.

881
00:38:41,580 --> 00:38:43,020
You just couldn't tell.

882
00:38:44,500 --> 00:38:46,340
(The rumors was getting more and more)

883
00:38:46,340 --> 00:38:47,740
(bizarre and indecent.)

884
00:38:48,060 --> 00:38:50,660
(She has become a bad student
in other people's eyes.)

885
00:38:57,540 --> 00:38:59,860
Fang Lu, help me inform our class.

886
00:39:00,100 --> 00:39:01,300
The practice for the opening ceremony

887
00:39:01,300 --> 00:39:03,320
of the sports meeting
on Saturday morning has been cancelled.

888
00:39:03,320 --> 00:39:04,660
There's no need to assemble at the gym.

889
00:39:04,660 --> 00:39:07,300
Inform the class to assemble

890
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:09,780
in front of the High School Hall
at 8:00 AM to listen

891
00:39:09,780 --> 00:39:11,980
to the speech
of the college entrance exam's top scorer.

892
00:39:12,460 --> 00:39:13,300
Okay.

893
00:39:13,460 --> 00:39:15,300
You must inform every student.

894
00:39:15,660 --> 00:39:16,500
Okay.

895
00:39:19,620 --> 00:39:20,460
Right.

896
00:39:22,180 --> 00:39:23,580
Why do you draw an arrow here?

897
00:39:24,180 --> 00:39:25,180
Fine, I won't.

898
00:39:30,180 --> 00:39:31,180
Will she come or not?

899
00:39:31,460 --> 00:39:32,300
Bro, she's here.

900
00:39:37,580 --> 00:39:39,660
Fang Lu, have a banana.

901
00:39:40,580 --> 00:39:41,460
Leave me alone.

902
00:39:41,550 --> 00:39:42,940
Or I'll find someone to beat you up.

903
00:39:43,260 --> 00:39:44,940
Please, be nicer to me.

904
00:39:45,260 --> 00:39:46,740
I'll treat you.

905
00:39:58,740 --> 00:40:01,020
There's a new transfer student
in our class.

906
00:40:01,340 --> 00:40:02,820
She's quite pretty.

907
00:40:03,660 --> 00:40:06,620
Go bother her.

908
00:40:09,140 --> 00:40:11,100
The one in the red dress?

909
00:40:24,660 --> 00:40:26,100
(Wu Xiuya didn't know)

910
00:40:26,220 --> 00:40:27,900
(the meeting place had changed.)

911
00:40:28,260 --> 00:40:30,820
(Fang Lu informed every classmate
by phone.)

912
00:40:31,180 --> 00:40:32,620
(But she didn't tell her.)

913
00:40:55,940 --> 00:40:56,780
There you are.

914
00:40:57,540 --> 00:40:58,380
Where's your dress?

915
00:40:59,140 --> 00:40:59,980
Who are you?

916
00:41:00,860 --> 00:41:02,860
Mao Biao,
a third grader from Class 7.

917
00:41:03,380 --> 00:41:04,260
Let's be friends.

918
00:41:04,860 --> 00:41:05,740
You don't know me?

919
00:41:07,700 --> 00:41:09,290
Why should we be friends?
I don't even know you.

920
00:41:09,290 --> 00:41:10,500
Now we know each other.

921
00:41:10,620 --> 00:41:13,620
Come, let's go watch tapes
at the video club.

922
00:41:14,260 --> 00:41:15,660
We can also do karaoke.

923
00:41:16,260 --> 00:41:17,180
Feng Xiaojuan.

924
00:41:17,180 --> 00:41:18,020
Yes.

925
00:41:18,660 --> 00:41:19,660
Han Liya.

926
00:41:19,660 --> 00:41:20,500
Yes.

927
00:41:20,540 --> 00:41:21,380
Fang Lu.

928
00:41:21,660 --> 00:41:22,500
Yes.

929
00:41:22,780 --> 00:41:23,660
Wu Xiuya.

930
00:41:23,660 --> 00:41:25,780
(Hall)

931
00:41:25,780 --> 00:41:26,600
Wu Xiuya!

932
00:41:26,600 --> 00:41:28,220
- Where's Wu Xiuya?
- Hasn't she arrived?

933
00:41:28,260 --> 00:41:29,100
Wu Xiuya!

934
00:41:29,380 --> 00:41:30,340
Let go of me!

935
00:41:30,580 --> 00:41:32,780
Help! Help!

936
00:41:33,450 --> 00:41:34,760
What are you doing? Let go of her.

937
00:41:34,760 --> 00:41:35,660
What are you doing?

938
00:41:35,660 --> 00:41:37,980
Kid, it's none of your business.
Go away.

939
00:41:38,220 --> 00:41:39,260
She's my classmate.

940
00:41:39,380 --> 00:41:40,620
How's that not my business?

941
00:41:41,140 --> 00:41:42,180
Stay out of trouble.

942
00:41:42,220 --> 00:41:43,540
I'll report to the teacher.

943
00:41:44,540 --> 00:41:45,660
Kid.

944
00:41:45,660 --> 00:41:46,820
Go away!

945
00:42:21,180 --> 00:42:23,180
(At this moment, Wu Xiuya had no idea)

946
00:42:23,620 --> 00:42:26,180
(that this fight would be)

947
00:42:26,420 --> 00:42:28,060
(an important turning point
in her life.)

948
00:42:33,820 --> 00:42:34,660
Look!

949
00:42:34,660 --> 00:42:36,500
Four students are penalized.

950
00:42:36,600 --> 00:42:38,830
(Zhu Haiyang, Shi Ye, Lv Dongqing, Wu Xiuya)
Is she the new student?

951
00:42:39,180 --> 00:42:40,020
What happened?

952
00:42:40,260 --> 00:42:41,100
Why do they take away

953
00:42:41,100 --> 00:42:42,980
the class prize flag?

954
00:42:43,420 --> 00:42:44,860
It's all because of Wu Xiuya.

955
00:42:45,180 --> 00:42:46,220
If it weren't for her,

956
00:42:46,460 --> 00:42:47,980
our class wouldn't be penalized.

957
00:42:48,260 --> 00:42:50,460
Right.
She even dragged the monitor down.

958
00:42:50,620 --> 00:42:52,660
I spent all that money to transfer you
to No.7 Middle School.

959
00:42:52,820 --> 00:42:54,140
That's how you reward me?

960
00:42:55,540 --> 00:42:56,980
You embarrass me!

961
00:42:58,180 --> 00:42:59,180
You are a girl.

962
00:42:59,660 --> 00:43:01,180
Behave yourself!

963
00:43:01,300 --> 00:43:02,740
Why are you messing around with boys?

964
00:43:03,620 --> 00:43:04,940
How shameless!

965
00:43:05,220 --> 00:43:06,220
I wasn't.

966
00:43:08,180 --> 00:43:09,660
You even learned to talk back at me!

967
00:43:11,220 --> 00:43:13,100
Look! How your mom has spoiled you!

968
00:43:13,300 --> 00:43:14,500
You are a girl.

969
00:43:14,660 --> 00:43:16,020
Learn to admit your mistakes!

970
00:43:16,020 --> 00:43:17,050
That's all you need to do.

971
00:43:18,100 --> 00:43:20,020
I will correct your bad habit.

972
00:43:23,460 --> 00:43:25,620
Tell me. Will you correct yourself?

973
00:43:26,660 --> 00:43:27,540
Speak up!

974
00:43:28,660 --> 00:43:29,660
I did nothing wrong.

975
00:43:29,660 --> 00:43:30,980
I was wronged.

976
00:43:32,180 --> 00:43:33,860
I just didn't please them.

977
00:43:33,860 --> 00:43:35,180
I didn't do what other people do.

978
00:43:35,300 --> 00:43:36,780
You're still acting tough, aren't you?

979
00:43:36,900 --> 00:43:38,100
You're not correcting yourself?

980
00:43:41,540 --> 00:43:42,460
Alright, then!

981
00:43:46,200 --> 00:43:47,220
Will you correct yourself?

982
00:43:47,320 --> 00:43:50,460
I didn't do anything wrong.

983
00:43:55,820 --> 00:43:56,740
Mom.

984
00:43:57,740 --> 00:43:59,060
Mom, help me!

985
00:43:59,060 --> 00:44:00,780
Talk to dad.

986
00:44:01,060 --> 00:44:02,860
Messing around with boys!

987
00:44:03,020 --> 00:44:04,940
- Playing basketball!
- I didn't.

988
00:44:05,860 --> 00:44:06,680
Mom.

989
00:44:06,680 --> 00:44:07,660
You're acting tough, huh?

990
00:44:07,660 --> 00:44:09,180
I'm so mad at you.

991
00:44:09,260 --> 00:44:10,220
Mom.

992
00:44:10,220 --> 00:44:12,060
How dare you play basketball with boys?

993
00:44:13,020 --> 00:44:14,820
Don't you ever touch basketball again!

994
00:44:16,140 --> 00:44:18,060
Let's see which one of us is tougher.

995
00:44:19,340 --> 00:44:20,740
You're such a trouble.

996
00:44:28,260 --> 00:44:30,540
Dad.

997
00:44:30,660 --> 00:44:33,540
I did nothing wrong.

998
00:44:35,380 --> 00:44:36,860
Can I not say that?

999
00:44:42,100 --> 00:44:42,940
Sure.

1000
00:44:43,220 --> 00:44:45,060
Let me do it for you.

1001
00:44:49,180 --> 00:44:50,180
I'll say it myself then.

1002
00:45:08,060 --> 00:45:09,060
Are you feeling better?

1003
00:45:10,660 --> 00:45:11,540
The class is ready.

1004
00:45:14,500 --> 00:45:15,340
Shi Ye.

1005
00:45:19,340 --> 00:45:20,180
What?

1006
00:45:21,820 --> 00:45:22,660
Mr. Mu.

1007
00:45:25,750 --> 00:45:26,780
I'd like to change a seat.

1008
00:45:29,060 --> 00:45:29,900
Why?

1009
00:45:33,260 --> 00:45:34,660
Sitting here affects my study.

1010
00:45:45,060 --> 00:45:46,620
Sit down first. The class has begun.

1011
00:45:52,660 --> 00:45:54,020
Don't be too upset.

1012
00:45:54,420 --> 00:45:55,860
It will be better after a while.

1013
00:45:56,420 --> 00:45:58,220
No, I did nothing wrong.

1014
00:45:58,660 --> 00:45:59,980
I couldn't stomach this.

1015
00:45:59,980 --> 00:46:02,060
I should let everyone know
that I did nothing wrong.

1016
00:46:02,180 --> 00:46:03,980
How can you make them understand?

1017
00:46:03,980 --> 00:46:06,180
You can't talk to all of them.

1018
00:46:06,380 --> 00:46:07,620
Forget it.

1019
00:46:07,820 --> 00:46:09,300
Study hard.

1020
00:46:09,300 --> 00:46:11,020
Then they won't be mean to you.

1021
00:46:12,140 --> 00:46:14,740
(Self-review, Wu Xiuya,
Class 3, Grade 11.)

1022
00:46:40,180 --> 00:46:41,020
Sit there.

1023
00:46:49,180 --> 00:46:50,300
Dean, I'll take my leave.

1024
00:46:50,300 --> 00:46:51,540
- Thank you.
- No need.

1025
00:46:58,740 --> 00:46:59,660
Dear teachers,

1026
00:47:00,260 --> 00:47:01,220
dear students,

1027
00:47:01,780 --> 00:47:03,100
three days ago,

1028
00:47:03,660 --> 00:47:05,820
a fight broke out

1029
00:47:05,820 --> 00:47:07,740
in our school.

1030
00:47:08,940 --> 00:47:11,060
Students from Class 3, Grade 11,

1031
00:47:11,540 --> 00:47:14,740
and those from Class 3 and Class 5,
Grade 12

1032
00:47:15,300 --> 00:47:16,940
are all involved.

1033
00:47:18,100 --> 00:47:20,660
This is a serious incident.

1034
00:47:22,180 --> 00:47:25,260
The school has taken serious actions

1035
00:47:25,500 --> 00:47:27,380
against the involved students.

1036
00:47:28,100 --> 00:47:30,180
Between today's classes,

1037
00:47:30,660 --> 00:47:32,260
all faculty and students

1038
00:47:32,540 --> 00:47:34,740
will not attend the setting-up exercise.

1039
00:47:35,620 --> 00:47:37,340
Let's all stay in the classrooms.

1040
00:47:38,020 --> 00:47:39,260
Let's listen

1041
00:47:39,260 --> 00:47:42,060
to Wu Xiuya's self-review.

1042
00:47:51,660 --> 00:47:55,540
(Ningxi No.7 Middle School)

1043
00:47:55,540 --> 00:47:56,380
I'm...

1044
00:47:59,380 --> 00:48:00,230
I'm...

1045
00:48:00,260 --> 00:48:03,460
I'm Wu Xiuya from Class 3, Grade 11.

1046
00:48:04,620 --> 00:48:06,180
On April 17th,

1047
00:48:06,260 --> 00:48:08,050
I left my classmates without permission,

1048
00:48:08,050 --> 00:48:09,200
Dean, I need to tell you something.

1049
00:48:09,260 --> 00:48:11,100
causing our monitor Shi Ye

1050
00:48:11,340 --> 00:48:14,100
to have a confrontation
with the third grader Mao Biao.

1051
00:48:14,260 --> 00:48:15,500
This severely harms

1052
00:48:15,500 --> 00:48:18,300
the school's discipline
and our class's reputation.

1053
00:48:19,180 --> 00:48:23,020
Hereby, I sincerely apologize

1054
00:48:24,300 --> 00:48:25,850
to all the students
and faculty of this school.

1055
00:48:34,780 --> 00:48:38,220
(Challenge Yourself to Break the Limit)

1056
00:48:56,140 --> 00:48:59,180
(No Smoking)

1057
00:48:59,180 --> 00:49:01,260
First, I admit that I was wrong.

1058
00:49:01,260 --> 00:49:02,650
- But I have to
- Wu Xiuya, open the door.

1059
00:49:02,650 --> 00:49:04,170
- explain the whole incident.
- Open the door!

1060
00:49:04,340 --> 00:49:05,820
Rumor runs in the school

1061
00:49:06,100 --> 00:49:07,690
that they fought because of me.

1062
00:49:11,940 --> 00:49:12,860
I went to the gym

1063
00:49:12,860 --> 00:49:14,140
because I hadn't been informed

1064
00:49:14,140 --> 00:49:15,660
that the rehearsal was cancelled.

1065
00:49:15,800 --> 00:49:17,540
But the teacher didn't listen
to my reasons.

1066
00:49:17,580 --> 00:49:19,540
They believed
that I gave rise to all this.

1067
00:49:19,740 --> 00:49:21,660
What does that mean?

1068
00:49:22,140 --> 00:49:24,060
Am I an alarm for them
to get up in the morning?

1069
00:49:28,140 --> 00:49:29,860
Yeah, Mao Biao did get up because of me.

1070
00:49:30,180 --> 00:49:32,180
He's been waiting for me
in the gym since 8:00 AM.

1071
00:49:32,790 --> 00:49:33,640
It's 8:00 AM!

1072
00:49:33,660 --> 00:49:35,660
I've never seen a punk rise up so early.

1073
00:49:39,060 --> 00:49:41,740
Thanks to my deskmate Shi Ye.

1074
00:49:42,100 --> 00:49:44,460
He came to my rescue
at the right moment.

1075
00:49:45,300 --> 00:49:46,780
But I didn't foresee

1076
00:49:47,740 --> 00:49:50,460
that he would ask to change his seat
the next day,

1077
00:49:50,780 --> 00:49:52,020
saying that

1078
00:49:52,060 --> 00:49:54,500
sitting there would affect his study.

1079
00:49:55,020 --> 00:49:56,780
How does your seat affect your study?

1080
00:49:57,100 --> 00:49:58,980
You rely on feng shui to study?

1081
00:49:59,340 --> 00:50:02,020
Your mom must be a sorcerer
instead of a teacher.

1082
00:50:03,940 --> 00:50:05,660
Be quiet!

1083
00:50:10,740 --> 00:50:11,620
Shi Ye's mom.

1084
00:50:12,340 --> 00:50:14,660
Don't worry.
I won't affect your son's study.

1085
00:50:14,820 --> 00:50:16,020
I'm not that pretty.

1086
00:50:16,300 --> 00:50:18,660
Don't think of me as the beauty,
Imperial Consort Yang.

1087
00:50:18,800 --> 00:50:19,660
Of course.

